"title":"Hadith on Humility: The Prophet chooses servitude, not kingship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 29, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Angel Gabriel was with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he looked towards the sky as an angel descended. Gabriel said, \u201cVerily, this angel has not come down since the day he was created.\u201d The angel said, \u201cO Muhammad, your Lord has sent\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33116,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/clean-mouth-for-angels-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":37106,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Siwak: Clean your mouth for the angels, the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, when the servant uses the toothstick and then stands to pray, an angel stands behind him and listens to his recitation. The angel draws near until his mouth coincides with his and nothing of the Quran comes out\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17132,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/12\/angels-dua-wudu-sleep\/","url_meta":{"origin":37106,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Angels supplicate for those who sleep with ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 12, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira report